CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: T1 Energy (NYSE: FREY) is an energy solutions provider building an integrated U.S. supply chain for solar and batteries. In December 2024, T1 Energy completed a transformative transaction, positioning the Company as one of the leading solar manufacturing companies in the U.S., with a complementary solar and battery storage strategy.
